snippet.title: Split: Sunstorm Update Trailer
snippet.description:
After countless resprites, remakes and rebalances, along with tons of new content, we're ready to announce the Sunstorm Update! This update, for players who already played the mod and who's yet to, is a truly fresh experience of one of our most beloved games, Terraria. Make sure to update the mod on Mod Browser on April 10th!

Terraria Forums page:
https://forums.terraria.org/index.php?threads/released-wip-the-split-mod.65235/

Join our Discord server to receive latest news and spoilers:
https://discord.gg/5eutHVCYMg

Support us on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/splitMod?fan_landing=true
